{"tid":2066751,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"拉舒福特寫信比英國下議會.首相批左1.2億比班英國學童有free午餐","createTime":"2020-06-16T13:12:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T03:05:39.000Z","uid":193217,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8dc1fadfd9dbabfd3eb7cf977c38c9f861ac265b","tid":2066751,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T13:12:50.000Z","msg":"官方消息，唐寧街採立拉舒福特提議，決定分配1.2億英鎊，為弱勢兒童免費提供學校餐。<br />\n<br />\n拉舒福特近日通過推特致信英國下議院，政府將在疫情封鎖期間繼續為弱勢青少年提供免費餐食，暑假期間延長低收入家庭的免費學校餐券發放。該教育券從三月開始實施，目的是在學校因封鎖而關閉時，幫助貧困家庭養活自己的孩子。<br />\n<br />\n英國政府早前拒絕了拉舒福特的提議，但今天宣佈在夏季開課時繼續免費提供學校餐食，其中包括針對130萬弱勢兒童的1.2億英鎊Covid餐券計劃。前所未有的時期英國家庭所面臨的問題。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n拉舒福特在推特上表示：&ldquo;我現在無法使用語言形容我的感受，看看我們能夠做些什麼吧，這就是2020年的英格蘭。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔該幫埋我地香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8146e88d2ddc11e6df02714f23e094103b8964ab","tid":2066751,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T13:25:54.000Z","msg":"push.咁撚好既野.連登仔當睇唔到呀"},{"pid":"22504a31673eedd33d0257e67b59af6ace998436","tid":2066751,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T13:30:17.000Z","msg":"Er...每人92鎊..."},{"pid":"aca2665bf61706a68f0700bd5e742f43820bbd48","tid":2066751,"uid":193217,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T13:35:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DcJcwLenMYU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDcJcwLenMYU&d=St%2FdMm9ieZWtYGJEeV6aa7c9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=4e078b10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DcJcwLenMYU</a>"},{"pid":"072d2973974d462fba5ff74309a6648f5878635c","tid":2066751,"uid":165711,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"22504a31673eedd33d0257e67b59af6ace998436","tid":2066751,"